A Note to Our Community:
We built SPCast Media Edge to be a powerful, modern alternative to legacy streaming servers. We want the broadcasting community, hobbyists, and small stations to thrive, which is why we offer a generous Free Tier (up to 100 concurrent slots) completely free of charge. Enjoy the software! The formal legal terms below simply protect our intellectual property so we can continue developing this project for you.
