2. GRANT OF LICENSE AND USAGE TIERS
The Software is proprietary and closed-source. Upon your agreement to this EULA, the Licensor grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the Software as follows:

2.1 Free Tier (Community/Evaluation)
You may use the Software free of charge for personal, non-commercial, or commercial purposes, provided that the total concurrent capacity across your deployment does not exceed one hundred (100) audio slots, or five (5) video slots.

2.2 Enterprise / Commercial Tier
Any deployment, configuration, or environment that demands or handles more than one hundred (100) concurrent audio slots or five (5) concurrent video slots requires a valid and active commercial license issued directly by the Licensor. Using multiple connected free instances to bypass the slot limitation is strictly prohibited.

